race.comment: Super competitive heat of the country sprint series. VEXATIOUS DANCER (3) is hard to go past. Game in defeat in town at Morphettville fresh then out sped over at Moonee Valley last time. Back a long way in grade and will take catching around here. QUIK RHAPID (2) finished last fresh but blew the start and was never in it from there. Best form measures right up to this level and fitter for the run is worth another chance. SIR RANDOLPH (5) resumes and while yet to win fresh is well placed this level. Placed over 1200m when last resuming and expected to be in the finish. EL PASO CITIE (9) is another resuming. Goes well here and drawn to stalk the leaders throughout Will be tough to stop late. ELLIOTTO (6) resumes from a long break and is well placed here on best figures. Another who will be charging late.
